*Classification (ILAR)*:  
- Oligoarticular (≤4 joints in 6 mo)  
- Polyarticular (≥5 joints, RF+/−)  
- Systemic (fever, rash, organomegaly)  
- Enthesitis-related  
- Psoriatic arthritis  
- Undifferentiated  

