- General: physiotherapy, exercise, psychosocial support  
- Drugs: NSAIDs for pain → Methotrexate (DMARD of choice) → Biologics if resistant  
- Steroids: oral/intra-articular for severe/systemic manifestations  
- Ophthalmology follow-up for uveitis screening  

